📚 Web Scraping with BeautifulSoup – Books to Scrape

This project demonstrates basic web scraping techniques using BeautifulSoup, Requests, and Pandas.
I scraped data from the practice website Books to Scrape
 (a beginner-friendly site for learning web scraping), cleaned the extracted information, performed some basic data operations, and finally stored the processed results into a CSV file.

🚀 Features

Scraped book data (title, price, availability, etc.) from Books to Scrape

Cleaned and structured the raw HTML data into a usable format

Performed simple data analysis/manipulation using Pandas

Exported selected fields into a CSV file for further use

🛠️ Tech Stack

Python 🐍

BeautifulSoup4 – for parsing and navigating HTML

Requests – for making HTTP requests

Pandas – for data manipulation and storage
